## Description
<!-- What went wrong? -->
When browsing auctions (both logged-in and non-logged-in users), the pagination displays a second page. However, clicking Go to Page 2 shows the message "No auctions match your search."

## Steps to reproduce
1.Navigate to the Auction listing page.
2.Browse the available auctions.
3.Click Go to Page 2 in the pagination controls.
4.Observe the result.

## Expected behaviour
If there is only one page of auction results, only Page 1 should be displayed, or Page 2 should be disabled/hidden.

## Actual behaviour
Page 2 is displayed in the pagination controls. When clicked, the message "No auctions match your search." is shown.

